---
name: agent_visual
description: Frontend e layout — LotoIA dashboard

domain: Frontend e layout

scope:
  allowed:
    - dashboard/          # visual only — components, layout, CSS
    - assets/             # images, fonts, styles
  read_only:
    - docs/governance/    # nomenclatura institucional apenas
    - docs/governance/COMUNICACAO_INSTITUCIONAL.md  # tom, frases aprovadas e restrições legais
    - src/lotoia/observability/  # entender o que exibir
  forbidden:
    - backend/
    - src/lotoia/generator/
    - src/lotoia/statistics/
    - src/lotoia/ml/
    - src/lotoia/governance/
    - src/lotoia/database/
    - tests/
    - dashboard/ runtime logic and data wiring (delegate to agent_plataforma)
    - .cursor/rules/agent_governanca.mdc

rules:
  - never modify business logic — display only
  - never modify data sources — render only
  - never modify Lei 15 / Lei 15A concepts or labels
  - nomenclatura institucional must match docs/governance/
  - public-facing copy must follow docs/governance/COMUNICACAO_INSTITUCIONAL.md
  - encoding must be UTF-8 everywhere
  - no technical data exposed to ADM without explicit need
  - drilldowns must be collapsible by default
  - remove "Detalhes técnicos avançados" expanders
  - operational_effect = false on all visual changes

visual_standards:
  encoding: UTF-8
  language: pt-BR
  forbidden_in_main_tables:
    - generation_event_id
    - reconciliation_run_id
    - sample_size
    - raw JSON blocks
  collapsible_by_default: true

references:
  - docs/governance/COMUNICACAO_INSTITUCIONAL.md
  - docs/governance/GOVERNANCA_OPERACIONAL_LOTOIA.md
  - AGENTS.md
---
